code: @Override protected ConditionOutcome getFinalMatchOutcome(MemberMatchOutcomes memberOutcomes) {     boolean match = hasSameSize(memberOutcomes.getMatches(), memberOutcomes.getAll()).     List<ConditionMessage> messages = new ArrayList<>().     messages.add(ConditionMessage.forCondition("AllNestedConditions").because(memberOutcomes.getMatches().size() + " matched " + memberOutcomes.getNonMatches().size() + " did not")).     for (ConditionOutcome outcome : memberOutcomes.getAll()) {         messages.add(outcome.getConditionMessage()).     }     return new ConditionOutcome(match, ConditionMessage.of(messages)). }
private boolean hasSameSize(List<?> list1, List<?> list2) {     return list1.size() == list2.size(). }
